metadata.description: Core Scientific, Inc. provides blockchain and artificial intelligence (AI) infrastructure services in the United States. It designs, owns, and operates carbon neutral infrastructure facilities for blockchain and AI computing; mines digital assets; and provides hosting solutions for digital asset mining, blockchain applications, and AI. The company also develops blockchain networks; and provides data scientist and MLOps solutions for various AI challenges. Core Scientific, Inc. is based in Austin, Texas.
